ansport: Error while dialing dial tcp...\"` 和 `timed out waiting for server handshake`，尤其是在 `ShippingService` 上。\n\n3. **调用关系**\n   - 异常路径主要涉及 `checkoutservice->shippingservice`。这表明 `shippingservice` 是该调用链条中的潜在瓶颈。\n\n### 初步假设和验证\n根据以上分析，`ShippingService` 是异常的根本原因，因为:\n- 它的响应时间在异常期间显著增加。\n- 出现了大量与连接和握手超时相关的错误。\n\n### 输出格式 (JSON)\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Response time increased from 9347 ms to 23852273 ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ShippingService\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frequent connection and handshake timeout errors\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这种分析表明 `ShippingService` 处理延迟是此次异常事件的主要根因。我们可能需要进一步检查 `ShippingService` 的具体实例或网络连接问题，以确认此次延迟和错误的具体原因。", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "74a44ae7-81", "component": "shippingservice", "reason": "rrt_max increased severely causing service delay", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "TraceAnalysis(74a44ae7-81)", "observation": "check checkoutservice->shippingservice path with high rrt_max increase observed during fault window."}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(shippingservice)", "observation": "Detected rrt_max spike. Response time jumped 9347 ms to 23852273 ms."}, {"step": 3, "action": "LogSearch(shippingservice)", "observation": "Found frequent connection errors like timed out and handshake failures."}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
